Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[♪ opening theme song playing]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[creaking]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau exhales]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunting]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] As I thought,\Na challenge, indeed.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's as if we're fighting{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}multiple master swordsmen\Nat once.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}On top of the sheer number\Nof attacks,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}his reflexes and stamina\Nfar exceed those of any man.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}He's overpowering Stark.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If this becomes\Na battle of endurance,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-we are sure to lose.\N-[Stark grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] Should we retreat\Nand regroup?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}He's faster than us.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}He would chase us down.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] This is bad.\NFrieren was right.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can't read his attacks.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Only one option.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] That fool...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I told him to deflect\Nhis attacks.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You are mine.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU]\NHe took the hit intentionally?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Tough young man.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I am impressed.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You are far sharper\Nthan I supposed.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Be it slight, you created\Njust the opening I need.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's over, Revolte.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Of course, I remember you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How could I ever forget{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the partner of the last\Nfirst-class mage I slaughtered?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The situation was similar\Nto this one, no?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You bravely ventured forth\Nto slay my allies{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}while your partner defended\Nthe village.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}By the time that you returned\Nfrom your path of glory,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}there was absolutely nothing\Nyou could do for him.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't you want to know\Nhow your partner died?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Silence.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I should thank your\Nfallen colleague for teaching me{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}a valuable lesson\Nabout mankind.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Fine, then.\NI will silence you myself.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}In that case,\Nallow me to grant you{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}a final piece of advice.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Search the wreckage\Nmore carefully,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}you may well find a survivor.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] A child?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Enjoy your last breaths.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau grunts softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau thuds]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[JUNG] I did it!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Did you see me get him,\NLord Revolte? Praise me!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[REVOLTE] Well done.\NYou have my thanks.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU]\NMy judgment was clouded.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}My mind's eye focused\Non memories of him.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There couldn't have been\Na child.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That much\Nshould've been obvious.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It is just as your partner\Nillustrated for me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Humans will protect their young\Nno matter what it may cost.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau chuckles]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] Don't be so certain.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If that were true,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}there would be much more light\Nin the world{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}than I see today.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I haven't crossed paths\Nwith many fools willing to die{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}protecting children\Nthey've never met.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I've only known one.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Seems he was a kind boy.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I would wager\Nthat was his undoing.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's the same in every era.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kind mages always lead\Nthe shortest lives.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU]\NHe met a magnificent end.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[SERIE] So even you can speak\Nempty words.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Genau, you're an unpleasant man.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You don't possess\Na grain of kindness.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Never change that.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}As you command.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[REVOLTE] Though killing\Nbrings me no great pleasure...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I shall end your misery.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau scoffs]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}To think my final act{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}was one so horribly\Nout of character.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunting]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[REVOLTE] Gracious.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I have faced many a warrior,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and never have I\Nencountered a foe{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}who could withstand\Na direct blow{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}from one of my blades.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You can still move after that?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You would've been better off\Nplaying dead, you fool.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Then we would've lost.\N[grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And I don't give up so easily!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The winner of any battle\Nis the last man standing!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Perhaps you're not\Nthe good person{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I thought you were.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're simply an idiot.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Though I suppose\Nthere is some valor in that.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Let us venture into\Nthe jaws of death as one.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The closer that he brings us\Nto our demise,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the greater the catharsis\Nwe shall feel when we survive.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Somethin' to look forward to.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now, let's hurry up\Nand get there.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] What should I do?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mistress Frieren disappeared\Nat some point.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Getting to watch from afar\Nevery once in a while{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}is a relaxing treat.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HEMMUNG] Concealing your mana\Nwill not help you hide.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I meticulously crafted this fog\Nwith magic of my own.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It detects\Nand identifies targets{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}from the faintest trace\Nof mana.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Useful,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}as no living creature can\Nconceal their mana completely.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] Visibility is poor,\Nand he's blocking my attacks.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}He's a bad matchup for me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[METHODE]\NI can sense Miss Fern.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}She seems to be\Nstruggling as well.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's understandable,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}her opponent's magic is\Nunlike any I have faced before.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Medrozobalt.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's so important over there?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Your only opponent\Nright now is me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm aware.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[METHODE]\NThere is nothing unconventional{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}about this demon's\Nfighting style.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Her combat is steady\Nand technique tried-and-true.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}She defends while she attacks.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Her fundamentals are solid.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I cannot find\Nthe slightest opening.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I would be remiss to try\Nand face her head-on.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}In an ideal world,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Miss Fern and I would\Nwork together{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to bring them both down.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But it's likely this fog has{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}powerful mana-detection\Ncapabilities.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Unfortunate...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Miss Fern's stealth\Nis her greatest asset{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and she can't use it.\NMeaning...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}our situation would\Ngreatly improve{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}if this fog were removed\Nfrom the picture.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Time to get a little rough.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[SOLIDE] What's this?\NHer attack pattern changed.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I know this fighting style.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I have seen it before.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}These tactics are similar\Nto those used{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}by a demon hunting clan\Nwho lived on the Plateau.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They dedicated their lives\Nto massacring my kind.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They were insane.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And it seems you may be, too.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You and I should be\Na good match.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now then, let's fight fair.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte yells]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] Such speed...\NI can't land a single spell.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}His movements are no longer\Nmasterful and measured.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They're savage\Nand erratic, like those{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}of a mindless predator.\N[grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau chokes]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] Despite the grievous\Nwounds we dealt,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}he fights on undaunted.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}His resilience is superhuman,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and his stamina\Nis seemingly inexhaustible.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If this keeps drawing on,\Nhe'll beat us by attrition.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte scoffs]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Genau, his swords!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If they can fracture,\Nthey can shatter!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They have grown brittle.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It appears he's\Nlost the essential focus{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to maintain the mana\Nhis many weapons require.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just three left!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[SOLIDE] Strange.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What is this dichotomy?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Her attacks\Nare undoubtedly ferocious,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but I sense no bloodlust\Nbehind them.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[METHODE] My...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You really are astute.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Though I fear the speed\Nof your notice{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}leaves a lot to be desired.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I've already finished\Nanalyzing this pesky fog.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}When all one knows is warfare,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the only spells they learn\Nare those for combat.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Were it any other member\Nof my clan{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}standing here before you,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}you would certainly defeat them,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}for they lack\Na fundamental insight.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Magic is incredibly fun.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Methode blows]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[METHODE] Erilfrachte.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HEMMUNG] They cleared the fog.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How pointless.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can just as easily\Nsummon it again.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now where has that girl\Nrun off to?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[SOLIDE]\NHemmung's mana vanished.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[SOLIDE] An attack?\NWhere'd it come from?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Zoltraak.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[SOLIDE] She's so far!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Methode chuckles softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] The trajectory\Nof a long-distance shot{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}from outside the range\Nof detection{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}cannot be predicted.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Impressive. Truly.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Fern sighs]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'd really rather not fight\Nsuch a difficult fight again.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte yelling]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunting]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just two more left to go!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] One!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte yelling]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark yells]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're disarmed. It's done.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Only humans would see\Nempty hands as harmless{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}when they're weapons\Njust the same.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Your fatal assumption was\Nto believe me rendered blunted{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}without the boon of my blades.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now victory is mine.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] Fatal assumption.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I think you'll find\Nboth our species{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}are capable of those.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You clearly have no idea\Nhow tenacious my kind can be.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[REVOLTE] Huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte gasps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Cleaving Light!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Revolte grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[Revolte yells]\N-Now, Digardnacht.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] For what it's worth,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}you seem like\Na good person to me, too.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're still trying\Nto defend the village,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}even after it's been destroyed.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I couldn't do that.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There, see?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're still here\Ntrying to save me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I knew it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're a good guy after all.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau groans]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[grunting]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[breathing heavily]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[straining]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We live to meet again.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I really am incapable\Nof dying properly, aren't I?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It would seem that way.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] Enough, I can move.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How is Stark?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[METHODE] A little worse\Nfor wear maybe.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But he'll live\Nto fight another day.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}When I arrived, I prioritized\Nhealing him over you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[gasps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] I see.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Are you displeased?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] No. He conducted himself\Nsurprisingly well.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If you wish to linger,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Miss Frieren's party\Nwill be staying in the village{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}while he recovers.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Good. I'm practically\Nback to baseline.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] He's doing push-ups.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}He's a real marvel of nature.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Or perhaps a freak of it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're so mean to me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[METHODE]\NMiss Frieren, I couldn't help{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but notice your party\Nis lacking a priest.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Once this request\Ndraws to a close,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'll have a fair bit\Nof free time on my hands.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I could accompany you,\Nshould you wish it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Fern gasps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The Northern Plateau\Ncan prove dangerous{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}without the spells of a priest.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No, we'll be okay.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can't cast any advanced level\Nhealing magic like you,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but I do know\Nsome lesser priest spells{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I could lean on in a pinch.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If we find ourselves\Nin serious trouble,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}we can always run away.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's worked pretty well so far.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Besides, prudent or not,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I think we'd like to keep our\Npriest slot open for a while.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You never know\Nwho you might bump into again.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And, well...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}For some reason,\NFern seems unhappy{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}whenever you're around us.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, goodness. Have I somehow\Nmade her hate me?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, reciprocated or not,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I still very much\Nlove you, Miss Fern.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And that adorably angry face\Nof yours.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Methode, the Chivalric Order\Nof Norm is here.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They're set to depart soon.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And we'll be accompanying them\Nback south.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Understood.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] It would seem{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}this is where\Nwe must say goodbye.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, Stark, how are your wounds?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Healed and ready\Nfor the next fight!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I see.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I owe you three a sizable debt.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}One I intend to repay.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[METHODE] Mister Genau.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Say it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Many thanks to you\Nfor all the help.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, right back at you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}May the both of us\Nlive long lives.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Genau chuckles]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[GENAU] Let's go.\N-Right.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Take care.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GENAU] Sure.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Till next we meet.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Hey,\Nwas it the right move{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to turn that down?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Methode's priest offer.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The sole priest this party\Nhas a place for is Sein.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, obviously.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But she's a pretty older woman.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't you think\NSein'll complain{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}that we didn't bring her along\Nwith us?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN]\NUse your head, Stark.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This party's "older woman"\Nspot is already filled.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark chuckles]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] How could I forget?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[♪ closing theme song playing]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.85,0:23:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] I suppose it shall\Ndepend on the reward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[overlapping chatter]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HEITER]\NI'm so bored, I could die.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[SAILOR] I've looked up to him\Never since I was a child.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:23:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[FERN] What does it say?\N-[FRIEREN] " Himmel's memoirs."{\b0}
